file.name: parameters-mix-issue.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
paths:
  '/api/v1/{tenant_id}/values':
    parameters:
      - name: tenant_id
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
      operationId: 'values#index'
      parameters:
        - schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - activity
              - employee
          in: query
          name: 'filter[resource_type]'
          required: true
        - schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: number
          in: query
          name: 'filter[attribute]'
        - schema:
            type: string
          in: query
          name: 'filter[value]'
    post:
      operationId: 'values#create'
      responses:
        '201':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
      tags:
        - Attributes
    patch:
      summary: ''
      operationId: values#update
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
